args:
The young shoot shrivels 'neath the weight
of heavy snow,

the warmth of spring a thousand miles away.

Yet even after wilting, it dreams an everlasting
dream...

...of spring's glorious arrival.
Witness a dance from Hinomotoâ€”\nthe sprout that parts the snow!
When this dance's power has you in its\ngrasp...
...you can't move a muscle. Makes\nfinishing off fiends super easy!
That's how it's supposed to work, at least.
Ha... Haha... Hahaha...\nI-I'm so sorry to trouble you...
But my nerves seem to be getting the best\nof me. Could someone direct me to the\nnearest latrine?
Wait, yer takin' a bathroom break at\na time like this?!
He's always like thisâ€”hopeless when it\nmatters most.
Man, looks can be deceivin', huh?
Stand down, I beg of you. If you p-put any\nmore pressure on me...
...THEN YOU'LL BE IN FOR A WORLD OF\nHURT!
What're you gonna do if I lose control,\nhuh?!
So get out of my way, fiend!\nOUT. OF. MY. WAY!
Whoa. What's gotten into him now?
This is what happens when he snaps.
He loses control of himself\nand just goes berserk.
HEEEYAAAH! WANT SOME RICE?\nOR SOME BAMBOO?
HIYAAAH! URAAAH! TASTE MY BLADE!\nI JUST WANNA HAVE FUN!
Nice job, Hanabusa. You beat them all.
So, yeah, that's Hanabusa. He's all yours,\nRanzal. Have fun! Keep in touch! Mwah!
Fer Pete's sake. Do we have a sign on the\ncastle that says ï¼‚Crazy Folks Wanted,ï¼‚\nor what?
I can't believe I humiliated myself on my\nvery first day here. I'm so ashamed.
Now I'm doomed to have everyone talking\nabout me behind my back all over againâ€”\nconsigned to a life of embarrassment...
Look! It's Hanabusa! He's so dreamyâ€”but\nhave you heard what everyone's saying\nabout him?
That he's faint of heart and feels sick\nwhen he gets nervous? Yeah.
Hee hee. Isn't that cute? It makes me want\nto, like, protect him from the evils of the\nworld!
Wait, people AREN'T looking down on\nme?
*whistle* He sure turned into Mr. Popular\nlickety-split.
So it seems. He's a walking joke back in\nHinomoto.
...Wait, I get it! I get it now!\nI mean, just look at the guy.
He looks the same as ever to me.
What he looks like is the point!
He looks perfect, but deep down,\nhe's super weak!
That contrast is just killer! If ya ask me,\nain't many folks what can resist a guy\nlike that.
We're done for. He's gonna have the whole\ncastle in love with him before long!
Ha ha ha. I never would've thought of it\nthat way. Weird.
People here...DON'T dislike me?\nThey accept me as I am?\nI can hardly believe it.

The plan was to only remain here for
a short time. I was to dance in my
upcoming performance to spread
our culture, then leave. But now...

Lady Mitsuhide, I beseech you!
Let me stay in this castle for a
while longer. I've never felt so
welcome anywhere.
I mean...if you want. But what about\nyour dream back home?
He wants to perform the sacred offering\ndance to Amaterasuâ€”a role most coveted\nby any devotee of the dancing arts.
Is that honor not the ultimate goal of\nyour whole family back home?
I need some time to think.\nUrgh, not now, stomach...
Whoa there! ...Man, is he gonna be okay?\nGuy's paler than a freshly bleached sheet.
Well... He's got a lot on his shoulders.
Keep an eye on him for me, Ranzal.\nHe could use a friend.
Excuse me ma'am, where might I find\nthe latrine?
...Please, now is not the time\nto discuss whether I am ï¼‚cute.ï¼‚\nDisaster is imminent...! *gurgle*
